27:32.058 --> 27:33.090
Okay.

27:33.092 --> 27:36.227
- SkinnyMom1958.
- _

27:36.607 --> 27:38.296
Damn it, she changed it.

27:38.298 --> 27:40.498
Rebecca, you okay out there?

27:40.500 --> 27:42.033
Yeah, Mom, I'm fine.

27:42.035 --> 27:43.367
Uh, enjoy your soak.

27:43.369 --> 27:45.036
You deserve it after
that "left foot blue,

27:45.038 --> 27:46.849
right hand yellow" tumble.

28:02.941 --> 28:06.169
